    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me over the years. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it runs smoothly and is totally ready for its next big adventure with you! If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great and drives even better, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
